# Snapshot Ubuntu mirror — pinned to a fixed date so deb files are
# byte-identical across builds. Includes noble-updates and
# noble-security so mid-version bumps (e.g. systemd 8.12 → 8.14)
# resolve consistently. mkosi's auto-generated sources for
# `Mirror=` only enable `noble main`, which leaves the resolver
# with version-skew when packages reference each other tightly
# across release pockets. Adapted verbatim from
# ConferLabs/confer-image (which uses the same snapshot date).
Types: deb
URIs: https://snapshot.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/20260209T000000Z
Suites: noble noble-updates noble-security
Components: main restricted universe multiverse
Signed-By: /usr/share/keyrings/ubuntu-archive-keyring.gpg
